Available Mission Arcs (Chronicle 10 Entry Points)

The following missions are formally available at the opening of Chronicle 10. Selection of any arc will advance the chronicle timeline.

1. Icewall Expedition

Investigation of anomalous activity beneath a glacier

Likely ties to pre-Cataclysm ruins or elemental instability



2. Silvanesti Insertion

Covert extraction or intervention within an occupied elven kingdom

High-risk stealth and diplomatic consequences



3. Neraka Infiltration

Intelligence-gathering operation targeting Dragon Army strategic planning

Significant long-term impact on regional war trajectory





