Campaign Tone Moving Forward

Focus shifts from crisis response to deliberate strategic choice

Missions are no longer reactive; the party selects where pressure is applied

Stakes remain high but are no longer existential at session start

Moral weight, political consequence, and resource tradeoffs continue to matter

